+# .agent/evidence/054-verify-01.txt
+# Contract 054 verification entry 01 -- captured 2026-07-19, re-captured after the PR #34 review round (tier/blast_radius/merge_order omitted), anchored to phase base 15a30e1
+# ACCEPTANCE TEST: ANTI-VACUITY (phase base 15a30e1 = the F-055 merge / PR #33): at the base the template held the {{TIER}} placeholder and did NOT validate against the schema, and fixtures_self_test had no template-schema guard.
